The '''''Rasvin''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]]. It was tasked with bringing a new [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] unit to the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]]. Although the frigate came under attack by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]], its [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] were able to drive off the Rebels and the freighter delivered the new hyperdrive unit safely.

